Environment set by travis-ci:
TRAVIS_REPO_SLUG : Account/Repo
TRAVIS_BUILD_NUMBER : The number of the current build
TRAVIS_COMMIT : The commit that the current build is testing

TRAVIS_BANCH : Name of the curent branch
DOXYFILE1..3 : The 3 Doxygen configuration files to handle
